  "title": "Front Desk/ Dental Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Job Responsibilities:</p>\n<p>- Counter duties such as booking of appointments, answering phone calls and enquiries, cashiering, submission of claims, scanning of documents</p>\n<p>- Daily, weekly and monthly reporting to management</p>\n<p>- Assisting dentists in managing the clinical treatment of patients</p>\n<p>- Preparing patients for dental work and providing excellent patient care</p>\n<p>- Helping with infection control by sterilizing and disinfecting instruments, setting up instrument trays, preparing materials and assisting with dental procedures</p>\n<p>- Recording treatment information in patient records</p>\n<p>- Exposing dental x-rays from dental diagnostics</p>\n<p>- Providing postoperative instructions as directed by the dentists</p>\n<p>- Upkeep and maintain dental equipment, facilities and facade</p>\n<p>- Forming preliminary impressions for study casts and occlusal registrations for mounting study casts</p>\n<p>- Ordering dental supplies and maintaining dental equipment inventory</p>\n<p>- Receiving and recording dental supplies, liaison with suppliers</p>\n<p>- Fabricating temporary restorations and custom impressions from preliminary impressions</p>\n<p>- Other ad-hoc duties</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Requirements:</p>\n<p>- Experience in using computer such as Google Drive and software such as Clinic Assist</p>\n<p>- Good written and verbal communication skills</p>\n<p>- Possess professional appearance and attitude</p>\n<p>- Able to provide excellent patient care and is patient</p>\n<p>- Able to work as a team and individually at the same time</p>\n<p>- Experience/ Non-experienced, on-the-job training provided</p>\n<p>- Able to travel between clinics</p>",
